dmca.title: Court-ordered TRO
dmca.body:
[Private]:

Please find attached "Order to Show Cause and Temporary Restraining Order" issued by Judge Dufficy of the Marin County Superior Court in Case No. CV 052451. The Order is self-explanatory with respect to its parameters.

Because every day that this defamatory material regarding Mr. [private] remains available for public consumption, Mr. [private]'s damages increase, thus, time is of the essence. Accordingly, your prompt action in this will be greatly appreciated.

Sincerely,
[signature]
[Private]
<hr>
...
IT IS FURTHER ORDERED that pending the hearing on this Order to Show Cause, the Defendant, [private] , individually and d/b/a NATIONAL CHECK FRAUD CENTER, and his agents, employees, representatives, and all other persons acting in concert or participating with him, including, by way of illustration, and not in limitation, all Internet Services Providers, including GOOGLE.COM, be, and hereby are enjoined from disseminating via the Internet or otherwise any information about [private]; and
...
